 <div align="center">
      <h1>
            <b>Delete Peak(s)</b>
      </h1>
      <hr />
	  </div>
	  <div >
	  <div style="padding-top: 10px" align="center">
	  <h3>
	  Method 1
	  </h3>
	  </div>
	   <div align="center">
	  <img src="InterSpec_resources/static_text/images/DeletePeak1-1.png"  class="imageBorder" style="max-width:40%; max-height:300px;" />
	  <img src="InterSpec_resources/static_text/images/DeletePeak1-2.png"  class="imageBorder" style="max-width:40%; max-height:300px;" />
	  </div>
	  <div style="padding-top: 10px" align="center">
      <u>Hold</u> <b><kbd>SHIFT</kbd></b> and <u>left-click drag</u> over the ROI to erase the identified peak(s).  
      </div>
	  <div style="padding-top: 10px" align="center">
	  <h3>
	  Method 2
	  </h3>
	  </div>
   <div align="center">
	  <img src="InterSpec_resources/static_text/images/DeletePeak2-1.png"  class="imageBorder" style="max-width:40%; max-height:300px;" />
	  <img src="InterSpec_resources/static_text/images/DeletePeak2-2.png"  class="imageBorder" style="max-width:40%; max-height:300px;" />
	  </div>
	  <div style="padding-top: 10px" align="center">
      <u>Right-click</u> on a highlighted peak and <u>select</u> the &#34;<b>Peak Editor</b>&#34;. In the <b>Peak Editor</b> dialog, <u>select</u> &#34;<b>Delete</b>&#34; from the bottom right of the window. 
      </div>
	  <div style="padding-top: 10px" align="center">
	  <h3>
	  Method 3
	  </h3>
	  </div>
	   <div align="center">
	  <img src="InterSpec_resources/static_text/images/DeletePeak3-1.png"  class="imageBorder" style="max-width:40%; max-height:300px;" />
	  <img src="InterSpec_resources/static_text/images/DeletePeak3-2.png"  class="imageBorder" style="max-width:40%; max-height:300px;" />
	  </div>
	  <div style="padding-top: 10px" align="center">
      Show the tools tabs, <u>select</u> &#34;<b>Clear all Peaks</b>&#34; on the bottom left of the window, and <u>select</u> &#34;<b>Yes</b>&#34; in the small window that pops up. Note that this method will delete <i>all</i> identified peaks.
      </div>
	  <div style="padding-top: 10px" align="center">
	  <h3>
	  Method 4
	  </h3>
	  </div>
	   <div align="center">
	  <img src="InterSpec_resources/static_text/images/DeletePeak4-1.png"  class="imageBorder" style="max-width:40%; max-height:300px;" />
	  </div>
	  <div style="padding-top: 10px" align="center">
      <u>Right-click</u> the identified peak and <u>select</u> &#34;<b>Delete Peak</b>&#34; in the dialog that pops up. 
      </div>
	  </div>